## STEP 3d — Additional SGX Capital Required to Close the Gap

At current blended SGX portfolio yield of ~4.0%, the goal requires a much larger income base. The table below shows how much **additional** SGX capital is needed at three blended yield assumptions, to generate the remaining SGD 81,418/year:

| Blended Yield | Additional Capital Required |
