**Strategic implication:** Reaching the goal entirely through new cash savings will take many decades at the current pace. The most practical path is a **gradual reallocation** of the growth book (GOOGL, CSPX) into SGX dividend stocks as those positions appreciate, supplemented by the SGD 1,000/month CSPX RSP building the growth base.

