A small position of 14 units (SGD 4,730). Amazon's AWS cloud and advertising segments remain strong growth engines, but at USD 263 the stock is pricing in significant future earnings expansion. No material news in the last 48 hours specific to earnings. Given the small position size there is no urgency to act. Hold.

