**CSPX — iShares Core S&P 500 UCITS ETF | USD 766.47 | Rating: ADD (continue RSP)**

CSPX is the largest single position at SGD 110,763 (48.7% of portfolio) and is the vehicle for the SGD 1,000/month FSMOne RSP. As an accumulating ETF it reinvests all S&P 500 dividends internally, giving efficient compounding with no SGX income contribution. This is the long-term wealth-building engine. Continue the RSP without change. Over a 10–20 year horizon, CSPX will be the primary source of capital that can eventually be partially redeployed into SGX dividend stocks as the income drawdown phase approaches.

