| **Mapletree Industrial Trust** | ME8U | >6.0% | Data centre + Singapore flatted factory diversification; yields above 6% after the March pullback; growth driver from AI-linked data centre demand |
| **Frasers Logistics & Commercial Trust** | BUOU | >6.0% | Pan-European + Singapore logistics REIT; 113 properties, SGD 6.9B portfolio; above-6% yield makes it one of the cheapest quality S-REITs currently |
| **OCBC Bank** | O39 | ~4.3% | SGD 2.5B capital return program targeted for completion by FY26; total FY25 dividend SGD 0.99/share; lower yield than DBS but buyback adds total-return kicker |
